e was introduced into England by the Normans, and this Latinized form is the one that normally occurs in medieval records, while the vernacular form <i>Maud</i> was the one in everyday use. <i>Matilda</i> was revived in England as a learned form in the 18th century."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Matilda was born about 1098, in Durham, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with Bernard de Balliol. She died in 1143, in Northumberland, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 46."},"et":{"about 1098–1143":"umbes 1098–1143","1095–1167":"1095–1167","1135–1204":"1135–1204","1098–1143":"1098–1143","1204":"1204","1135":"1135","1167":"1167","1143":"1143","1098":"1098","about 1135":"umbes 1135","about 1098":"umbes 1098","1095":"1095","Durham, England":"Durham, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Northumberland, England":"Northumberland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1098–1143":"noin 1098–1143","1095–1167":"1095–1167","1135–1204":"1135–1204","1098–1143":"1098–1143","1204":"1204","1135":"1135","1167":"1167","1143":"1143","1098":"1098","about 1135":"noin 1135","about 1098":"noin 1098","1095":"1095","Durham, England":"Durham, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Northumberland, England":"Northumberland, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1098–1143":"environ 1098–1143","1095–1167":"1095–1167","1135–1204":"1135–1204","1098–1143":"1098–1143","1204":"1204","1135":"1135","1167":"1167","1143":"1143","1098":"1098","about 1135":"environ 1135","about 1098":"environ 1098","1095":"1095","Durham, England":"Durham, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Northumberland, England":"Northumberland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Matilda est née environ 1098, à Durham, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Bernard de Balliol. Elle est décédée en 1143, à Northumberland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 46 ans."},"de":{"about 1098–1143":"um 1098–1143","1095–1167":"1095–1167","1135–1204":"1135–1204","1098–1143":"1098–1143","1204":"1204","1135":"1135","1167":"11